{"tid":977213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又一單】西貢年春街貨車撞婆婆 一地鮮血","createTime":"2019-01-11T04:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T04:38:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13f1df7f4436256001db66052297191941261d34","tid":977213,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"西貢年春街貨車撞婆婆 一地鮮血<br />\n<br />\n早上10時10分，一輛貨車在西貢年春街右轉期間，撞倒一名老婦。讀者林先生剛巧路過，見到滿頭白髮的婆婆，俯伏地上昏迷不醒，地上有大灘鮮血。救護員將她扶正時，見到傷者的左邊面頰血肉模糊，懷疑與地面磨擦過所致，她稍後由救護車送院搶救。"},{"pid":"3c2d3f97cd1f145830c5af77631aa0a845e73990","tid":977213,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190111/59129788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F59129788&d=48mk7pwonB40V2PL3zWGtp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6a273692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190111%2F59129788&h=5467ea45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190111/59129788</a>"},{"pid":"ba49b1b3b924280b2287fe2965822f8bd2580ba4","tid":977213,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d46b9a48f3860f594d67800ac6a27815e2e2a531","tid":977213,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"準備睇冇人性嘅連登仔嘲笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}